yhadithonline\/2020\/10\/20\/charity-true-wealth-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19217,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Acts of charity are true wealth in the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhich of you loves the wealth of his heirs more than his own wealth?\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, there are none of us but his own wealth is more beloved to him.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34488,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/20\/acts-of-charity-stored-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19217,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Only charity stored for the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe servant says: My wealth, my wealth! Verily, he only gets three from his wealth: he eats and it perishes, or he wears clothes and they degrade, or he gives in charity and it is stored\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32651,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/three-best-things-leave-behind\/","url_meta":{"origin":19217,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Three best things to leave behind after de